								<h2 class="single-excerpt"><p>From removing pesky rust stains to clearing-off itchy dandruff, here is a list of 10 amazing  home uses of lemon.</p>
</h2>
								<div class="KonaBody"><p>Aside from supplying the body with 60% of its recommended daily allowance of Vitamin C, lemon can be&nbsp; a useful and handy home partner! Read on to learn more about the ten home benefits lemon offers.</p>
<p><img src="http://s3.amazonaws.com/readers/2011/11/03/1alemon_1.jpg" alt="" width="375" height="500" /></p>
