<ul>
<li>Keep apples, avocados and bananas from turning brown! Just sprinkle a little lemon juice and it will do the trick. </li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Lemon juice is highly acidic it actually kills germs.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>A natural deodorizer due to its strong scent, lemon serves as a perfect cleaning agent. Freshen your garbage cans by occasionally throwing in some used lemons in them.&nbsp; </li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>A mixture of lemon juice and baking soda helps remove stains from plastic food storage containers. </li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Lemon juice mixed with salt (2:1 ratio) can rid rust stains.</li>
</ul>
