<li>An equal mixture of lemon juice and green tea makes a highly-flavored antioxidant blend.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Mix lemon juice with hot water is effective against constipation, indigestion, as well as heart burn.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Drinking several glasses of lemon juice during the day can lead to weight loss. </li>
</ul>
